    function logGAMainInteractions(_ref) {
        var eventLabel = _ref.eventLabel,
            action = _ref.action;
        var eventAction = { mainMenu: 'Main Menu', footer: 'Footer', languageSelected: 'Language Selected' }[action] || action;

        dataLayer.push({ event: 'GAEvent', eventCategory: 'Main Interactions', eventValue: 0, eventAction: eventAction, eventLabel: eventLabel });
    }

    jQuery(document).ready(function() {
        jQuery('.HeaderMenu a[data-title], .SidebarMenu a[data-title]').click(function() {
            logGAMainInteractions({eventLabel: jQuery(this).attr('data-title'), action: 'mainMenu'});
        });

        jQuery('.Footer__nav a').click(function() {
            logGAMainInteractions({eventLabel: jQuery(this).attr('data-title'), action: 'footer'});
        });

        jQuery('.LanguageSwitch').on('change', function() {
            var optionValue = jQuery(this).find('option:selected').text().trim();
            logGAMainInteractions({eventLabel: optionValue, action: 'languageSelected'});
        });

        jQuery('.wp-NativeLinkDropdown__select').on('change', function() {
            var optionValue = jQuery(this).find('option:selected').text().trim();
            logGAMainInteractions({eventLabel: optionValue, action: 'languageSelected'});
